{%- comment -%}
  ASR Outdoor — Product Trust Row
  Reassurance icons placed directly under the Add to Cart button.
  Also hides Dawn's broken "Couldn't load pickup availability" widget.

  HOW TO INSTALL (theme customizer, no code editor needed):
    1. Online Store -> Themes -> Customize.
    2. In the top dropdown, choose "Products" -> "Default product".
    3. In the left "Product information" section, click "Add block".
    4. Choose "Custom liquid".
    5. DRAG the new Custom liquid block so it sits RIGHT BELOW the
       "Buy buttons" block (i.e. just under Add to cart / Buy it now).
    6. Paste EVERYTHING in this file into the Custom liquid box.
    7. Save. It now shows on every product automatically.

  All facts here are confirmed true: ships from Bellingham WA warehouse,
  30-day returns, secure Shopify checkout, US-based seller.
{%- endcomment -%}

<style>
  /* Hide the broken local-pickup widget (we don't offer in-store pickup) */
  .product__pickup-availabilities,
  pickup-availability,
  pickup-availability-preview { display: none !important; }

  /* Hide the vague "Shipping calculated at checkout" caption under the price
     (our trust row already states shipping clearly) */
  .product__tax { display: none !important; }

  .asr-trust-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.2rem 1.6rem;
    margin: 1.6rem 0 0.4rem;
    padding-top: 1.6rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }
  .asr-trust-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    flex: 1 1 45%;
    min-width: 0;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: rgb(var(--color-foreground));
  }
  .asr-trust-item svg {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    width: 2.2rem;
    height: 2.2rem;
    color: #275333; /* ASR brand green */
  }
  .asr-trust-item span { font-weight: 500; }
  @media (min-width: 750px) {
    .asr-trust-item { flex: 1 1 40%; font-size: 1.4rem; }
  }
</style>

<div class="asr-trust-row" role="list" aria-label="Why buy from ASR Outdoor">
  <div class="asr-trust-item" role="listitem">
    {%- comment -%} truck {%- endcomment -%}
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M1 3h13v11H1z"/><path d="M14 7h4l3 3v4h-7z"/><circle cx="5.5" cy="18" r="1.8"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="18" r="1.8"/>
    </svg>
    <span>Ships from Bellingham, WA</span>
  </div>

  <div class="asr-trust-item" role="listitem">
    {%- comment -%} return arrow (rotate-ccw) {%- endcomment -%}
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
      <polyline points="1 4 1 10 7 10"/>
      <path d="M3.51 15a9 9 0 1 0 2.13-9.36L1 10"/>
    </svg>
    <span>30-Day Returns</span>
  </div>

  <div class="asr-trust-item" role="listitem">
    {%- comment -%} lock {%- endcomment -%}
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
      <rect x="4" y="10" width="16" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M8 10V7a4 4 0 0 1 8 0v3"/>
    </svg>
    <span>Secure Checkout</span>
  </div>

  <div class="asr-trust-item" role="listitem">
    {%- comment -%} shield/check {%- endcomment -%}
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M12 2l8 3v6c0 5-3.4 8.5-8 11-4.6-2.5-8-6-8-11V5z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/>
    </svg>
    <span>Trusted U.S. Seller</span>
  </div>
</div>
